This is the notes for Deleting rows

Lets take a look at deleting data
We use the DELETE FROM statement  

DELETE FROM:
used to delete records from a table 
We can optionally use a search condition to 
find the records that we want 

if we do not write the where clause this will delete all of 
records from the table selected

we can also use subqueries in this delete statement 
so if we wanted to delete all of the invoices for Myworks
we should find the client